title: Assassin's Creed Mirage Leaks - Kinda Funny Games Daily 08.30.22
description:
Greg and Blessing talk about new Assassin's Creed leaks, Immortality reviews, and Logitech's handheld device leaking.

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:08:00 - Housekeeping
A new Kinda Funny Podcast is up right now on Youtube.com/KindaFunny and podcast services around the globe.
Over on Youtube.com/KindaFunnyGames: there’s a new Xcast up! The crew talks about Xbox Series X prices and whether we could possibly ever see them go up.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: FargoBrady, GuyVee, & The Sabateur
The Roper Report  -
00:10:50 - The name of the next Assassin’s Creed game has seemingly leaked - Ed Nightingale @ Eurogamer
00:26:20 - Immortality Review Round Up
00:36:50 - Ad
00:39:10 - Logitech’s cloud gaming handheld leaks - Tom Warren @ The Verge
00:46:50 - European PlayStation players get more Platinums than US players, Sony reveals - Chris Scullion @ VGC
00:53:02 - Big Chungus Might Be Coming to MultiVersus - Ryan Leston @ IGN
00:59:00 - Out today
01:03:00 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:
Blessing and Greg
